Class Address

  • java.lang.Object
    • domain.Address
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Embeddable
public class Address
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is the embeddable class which is used in the rest of the classes for representing the Address as whole.This class contains attributes to further classify the address as line numbers, city, state, zip and country
    See Also:
